      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُ أَبَا جَعْفَرٍ اَلثَّانِيَ عَنِ اَلصَّبِيِّ مَتَى يُحْرَمُ بِهِ قَالَ «إِذَا اِثَّغَرَ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2899 - It was narrated from Ali ibn Mahziyar, from Muhammad ibn al-Fudhayl, who said:\nI asked Abu Ja'far al-Thani, Imam Muhammad al-Jawad (as) about when a child should be entered into the state of Ihram.\nImam (as) said: \"When they begin to grow teeth.\""
        ]
      }
    },
